| Layer          | Dev (EKS)                                  | Staging (AKS)                              | Prod (GKE)                                 | OpenShift (On-Prem)                   | Parity Rule & Enforcement                                      |
|----------------|--------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------|
| K8s Version    | 1.28                                       | 1.28                                       | 1.28                                       | 1.28 (OCP 4.14)                       | Must match exactly. Terragrunt `k8s_version` input locked.     |
| CNI Plugin     | Calico                                     | Calico                                     | Calico                                     | OVN-Kubernetes                        | Same network policy behavior. Helm chart pinned to v3.26.      |
| Node OS        | Ubuntu 22.04                               | Ubuntu 22.04                               | Ubuntu 22.04                               | RHEL 8                                | CIS Level 1 hardening via cloud-init + Project 1 runbook.      |
| CIDR Range     | 10.0.0.0/16                                | 10.1.0.0/16                                | 10.2.0.0/16                                | 192.168.0.0/16                        | Non-overlapping. BGP-exported via TGW/vWAN.                    |
| Storage Class  | gp3                                        | managed-premium                            | pd-ssd                                     | ocs-storagecluster                    | Same IOPS tier (3K). Helm `storageClass` override per env.     |
| IAM Binding    | IRSA                                       | Azure AD Pod Identity                      | GKE Workload Identity                      | OAuth + ServiceAccount                | Least-privilege pattern. Crossplane enforces.                  |
| Node Pools     | 2x t3.large                                | 2x Standard_B2s                            | 2x e2-medium                               | 4x Worker Nodes                       | Same CPU/mem ratio. Autoscaler min/max parity.                 |
| Add-ons        | Cert-manager, ExternalDNS, Metrics-server  | Cert-manager, ExternalDNS, Metrics-server  | Cert-manager, ExternalDNS, Metrics-server  | OpenShift Router, Prometheus Operator | Helm `addons` array identical across envs.                     |